 This package contains extra gtk themes for netrunner.


Package: netrunner-plymouth-theme-logo
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-label
Provides: plymouth-theme
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - netrunner theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default netrunner theme.
 
 
Package: netrunner-plymouth-theme-text
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plymouth, plymouth-theme-ubuntu-text
Provides: plymouth-theme
Replaces: plymouth (<< 0.8.1-1~)
Description: graphical boot animation and logger - netrunner-text theme
 Plymouth is an application that runs very early in the boot process
 (even before the root filesystem is mounted!) that provides a graphical
 boot animation while the boot process happens in the background.
 .
 This package contains the default netrunner-text theme used when no
 support for a graphical theme is found on your system.


Package: netrunner-ce-theme
Architecture: all
